OpenCSG
------------------------------------------
OpenCSG is a library that does image-based CSG rendering using OpenGL.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.5-1
  libGL1-19.1.6-1
  libGLEW2.1-2.1.0-1
  libX11_6-1.8-1
  libgcc1-11.3.0-1
  libopencsg1-1.5.1-1bl1
  libstdc++6-11.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.38-1
  cmake-3.20.0-1
  cygport-0.35.1-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  libGL-devel-19.1.6-1
  libGLEW-devel-2.1.0-1
  libQt5Core-devel-5.9.4-2
  libX11-devel-1.8-1
  make-4.3-1

Canonical website:
  https://www.opencsg.org/

Canonical download:
  https://www.opencsg.org/OpenCSG-1.5.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack OpenCSG-1.5.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./OpenCSG-1.5.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/OpenCSG-1.5.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/OpenCSG-1.5.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libopencsg1-1.5.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libopencsg-devel-1.5.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(OpenCSG)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/OpenCSG.README
  /usr/share/doc/OpenCSG/COPYING.txt
  /usr/share/doc/OpenCSG/README.md

(libopencsg1)
  /usr/bin/cygopencsg-1.dll

(libopencsg-devel)
  /usr/include/opencsg.h
  /usr/lib/libopencsg.dll.a

